Testing
~~~~~~~

For running tests and check the relative coverage:

.. code-block::

    coverage run --source hyo2 setup.py test

To get the test coverage report:

.. code-block::

    coverage report -m

and/or:

.. code-block::

    coverage html
    open html_cov/index.html
